*+
*  Name:
*     CCD1_NDFCM

*  Purpose:
*     Define CCDPACK NDF access common block.

*  Language:
*     Starlink Fortran 77

*  Type of Module:
*     Global variables include file.

*  Description:
*     This file defines the CCDPACK common block for containing the
*     primary locators to NDFs.

*  Authors:
*     PDRAPER: Peter Draper (STARLINK)
*     {enter_new_authors_here}

*  History:
*     31-OCT-1991 (PDRAPER):
*        Original version.
*     {enter_further_changes_here}

*-

*  Global Variables:

*  Define space for storing locators to NDFs.
      CHARACTER * ( DAT__SZLOC ) CCD1_TLOC( CCD1__MXNDF )

*  Number of locators stored in common
      INTEGER CCD1_NACC

*  Define separate common blocks for character variables.
      COMMON/ CCD1_NDFCM1 / CCD1_TLOC
      COMMON/ CCD1_NDFCM2 / CCD1_NACC
* $Id$
